00:14:53.850 --> 00:14:55.570
But then when we get more data, no!

00:14:55.570 --> 00:14:56.740
The bacteria are up here.

00:14:56.740 --> 00:14:58.610
They've passed that asymptote.

00:14:58.610 --> 00:15:00.090
Whereas this power law model,

00:15:00.090 --> 00:15:01.520
which says things are slowing down,

00:15:01.520 --> 00:15:03.220
