00:15:12.290 --> 00:15:14.290
It predicts sort of the future course

00:15:14.290 --> 00:15:16.090
of the evolutionary trajectory.

00:15:16.090 --> 00:15:17.800
And to me, that's kind of profound

00:15:17.800 --> 00:15:21.520
